page.title: 16BIOGRAPHY HOLBEACH DROVE
page.content: WE DO IN FACT HAVE A PERSONALITY IN THE VILLAGE - ALISON CAPES WHO IS GEEST GOLDEN GIRL. GEEST, WHO ARE THE MAIN EMPLOYEES IN THE AREA AND WHO ARE BASED IN SPALDING ARE A BIG CONCERN IN BANANAS! THEY IN FACT DEAL IN PRE PACKING FRUIT AND SALADS AND ALSO DEAL IN BULBS - MAINLY TULIPS - AND IN MAY OF EACH YEAR THEY HAVE A TULIP PARADE WHICH IS WELL KNOWN THROUGHOUT THE COUNTRY. THEY CHOOSE A GOLDEN GIRL FOR EACH YEAR AND THIS BEING THEIR JUBILEE YEAR - GOLDEN JUBILEE, ALISON IS TO HOLD THE TITLE FOR THESE CELEBRATIONS. WITH 1986 BEING THEIR 50th ANNIVERSARY ALISON WILL NO DOUBT ATTEND MANY FUNCTIONS AND MAYBE OPEN OUR OWN LOCAL FETES AND BAZAARS. SHE IS AN ADMINISTRATION CLERK IN GEEST PRODUCT MARKETING AND IS 18 YEARS OLD.
